{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Seek international action to resolve unrest in Colombia",
        "additional_details": "Colombia is going through moments of terror and anguish; we ask the UK Government to work with the international community, to condemn all acts of violence and intervene, however possible, to help put a stop to the bloodshed of so many lives. As a Colombian living in the UK, I beg you to make the current situation known, support it in whatever way you consider fit or advise of a course of action to take.",
        "background": "The Government needs to take urgent action to secure international support and intervention to resolve unrest in Colombia. Protests have resulted in a number of deaths already, and there are widespread reports of human rights abuses and censorship. International action is needed.",
